  "Purge du circuit secondaire du bloc ABS/ESP": {
   "width": 11940,
   "height": 9060,
   "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Purge du circuit secondaire du bloc ABS/ESP",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1320,
      "top": 0,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 9240
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 16.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": ". Pour r\u00e9aliser la purge du circuit secondaire du bloc hydraulique et afin de ne pas introduire d'air,  il faut:",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": -120,
      "top": 480,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 12480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-1- s'assurer que le circuit de freinage du v\u00e9hicule a \u00e9t\u00e9 purg\u00e9 par la m\u00e9thode de purge traditionnelle.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 840,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 12000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-5- appuyer fortement sur la p\u00e9dale de frein et tout en maintenant le pression sur celle ci lancer l'ordre de purge de la roue ARG.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,128,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 2520,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 11640
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-2- moteur coup\u00e9, apr\u00e8s 3 appuis sur la p\u00e9dale de frein, contr\u00f4ler la course de la p\u00e9dale qui doit \u00eatre correcte (p\u00e9dale dure).",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 1200,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 11760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-3- installer l'appareil de purge sur le bocal de liquide frein.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 1800,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-7- purger la roue ARG afin d\u00e9vacuer l'air dans ce circuit, puis refermer le purgeur",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,128,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 3480,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-8- appuyer fortement sur la p\u00e9dale de frein et tout en maintenant le pression sur celle ci lancer l'ordre de purge de la roue AVD.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,128,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 3840,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 11640
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-10- purger la roue AVD afin d\u00e9vacuer l'air dans ce circuit, puis refermer le purgeur",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,128,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 4800,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-11- appuyer fortement sur la p\u00e9dale de frein et tout en maintenant le pression sur celle ci lancer l'ordre de purge de la roue ARD.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,128,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 5160,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 11640
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-13- purger la roue ARD afin d\u00e9vacuer l'air dans ce circuit, puis refermer le purgeur",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,128,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 6120,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-14- appuyer fortement sur la p\u00e9dale de frein et tout en maintenant le pression sur celle ci lancer l'ordre de purge de la roue AVG.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,128,128)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 6480,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 11640
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-17- Contr\u00f4le final: Moteur coup\u00e9 et apr\u00e8s 3 appuis sur la p\u00e9dale de frein, contr\u00f4ler de nouveau la course p\u00e9dale qui doit \u00eatre correcte (p\u00e9dale dure)purger la roue AVG afin d\u00e9vacuer l'air dans ce circuit, puis refermer le purgeur",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(128,255,128)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 7920,
      "height": 1080,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-4- s'assurer que les vis de purge (purgeur) soient ferm\u00e9es.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 2160,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
